title: Foyle's War - Series 5 - Plan of Attack - Broken Souls - All
description:
Foyle's War - Series 5
----------------------

These are the compressed avi files of the three broadcast episodes from seriea 5 of Foyle's War.

The episodes are, in order, 'Plan of Attack', 'Broken Souls' and 'All Clear'.  The narrative takes us to the end of DCI Foyle's wartime career.  This uses the UK series/episode numbering.  The USA series/episode numbering is different.  See the IMBD page on Foyle's War: http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0310455/

Although the millions of fans of the series had hoped for a new series of "Foyle's Peace", it doesn't look like we're ever going to see it.

Technical stuff...

The files are compressed using AutoGordianKnot (http://www.autogk.me.uk/) and are XVID AVI files.  Each is about an hour and a half long.
